# Core Entity Standards Integration
- Pull tag/material standards from `Na__Common__DataLib__CoreSuEntityStandards`.
- Load via `Na__DataLib__CacheData.Na__Cache__LoadData(...)` from plugin modules.
- Treat DataLib JSON as source of truth for SketchUp naming standards.
- Use hardcoded defaults only as fallback when DataLib is unavailable.
